content: From here, you'll again have two diverging paths - one leading up to the left of the large tree in the village area, and a lower path down to the right. Annoyingly, both paths will lead to the same spot where the next boss is, and both routes have a Shrine, plus items worth getting.

The content is as follows:
From here, you'll again have two diverging paths - one leading up to the left of the large tree in the village area, and a lower path down to the right. Annoyingly, both paths will lead to the same spot where the next boss is, and both routes have a Shrine, plus items worth getting.
